## Limitations

This report primarily focuses on the positive economic impacts of immigration, and while it acknowledges the existence of challenges such as wage suppression in certain sectors, it does not delve deeply into these issues. Additionally, the data and studies referenced are subject to the limitations inherent in economic modeling and forecasting, which can be influenced by various external factors.

